{"tid":1629361,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"《林鄭七宗罪》","createTime":"2019-10-06T08:35:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T11:26:04.000Z","uid":104902,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"eedce221a2a896143fea657227617aebb75cecdd","tid":1629361,"uid":104902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T08:35:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">林鄭七宗罪</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一、企圖通過修例破壞一國兩制</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">二、損害香港法治、人權自由</span></strong><br />\n        i. 剝奪港人遊行集會自由<br />\n        ii. 否認香港自治<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">三、假意對話，無意正面回應香港人的五大訴求，使民怨升溫</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">四、縱容警察濫權濫捕、危害市民安全</span></strong> (例子不能盡錄)<br />\n        i.   實彈射中兩名學生<br />\n        ii.  持槍進入醫院範圍<br />\n        iii. 拒絕醫護人員為示威者急救<br />\n        iv. 射擊記者<br />\n        v.  殘酷對待被捕示威者<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">五、縱容黨鐵與警察合作</span></strong><br />\n        i.   隨意罷駛及封站，影響交通<br />\n        ii.  運送防暴到各區拘捕示威者<br />\n        iii. 仍未公開831太子站當晚閉路電視片段<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">四、繞過立法程序，引用緊急法硬推禁蒙面法</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">五、特區政府形象破滅，國際金融中心地位動搖</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">六、製造社會恐慌和不安，嚴重危害香港市民精神健康</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">七、管治無能，導致多名抗爭者犧牲性命以明其志</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">香港人，請不要習慣這醜惡極權的統治。面對不公義的社會制度時，請緊記我們所擁抱的核心價值。<br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可</span></span>"},{"pid":"a7d36150750e162e22bb1e127c14e9ed31de507e","tid":1629361,"uid":104902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T08:37:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b730c1bc8e280319e2ca1b2d8bbc9c27a58472e5","tid":1629361,"uid":104902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T08:41:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">香港人，反抗</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd02befa7b594be9c1be49789e7df033128c4fd8","tid":1629361,"uid":323008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T10:35:50.000Z","msg":"聯絡英國政府要求英國取消林奠丈夫同她2位兒子的英國國藉，及遺返香港，並取消她兒子的學歷。"},{"pid":"d95d9a97e8713bdb46744f6aeebdc1d7705231f1","tid":1629361,"uid":104902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T10:43:23.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1516f5fe8002c3c20e81a3a4db6e041735b44a8f","tid":1629361,"uid":193215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T10:43:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff26833c83aaf07e07f954e078de561c979925ee","tid":1629361,"uid":104902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T10:44:39.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd697f75d2c4df091278f10ed76d6359e0d51e10","tid":1629361,"uid":47659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T10:53:11.000Z","msg":"不要說維園見港島見, 試著說自己區要人今晚散步<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">自己區要人今晚散步 <br />\n急徵裝修技工<br />\n急徵雨傘兵擋雨<br />\n急徵物資兵<br />\n18區都要人啊</span>"},{"pid":"36e11a811dbb7e0805279965340606532c0fe8ae","tid":1629361,"uid":237465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:16:26.000Z","msg":"7 條罪咁少 ?"},{"pid":"ae2e14151719a2bbcf2aa6aeb1d51715f4c51210","tid":1629361,"uid":104902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"36e11a811dbb7e0805279965340606532c0fe8ae","tid":1629361,"uid":237465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:16:26.000Z","msg":"7 條罪咁少 ?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:26:04.000Z","msg":"其罪罄竹難書<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}